column5: What are the limits of fish you can keep per day as well as their size?Walleye of coarse
We have two types of licenses. Conservation license means u can keep 2 walleye and only one can be larger than 24.8"Sportsman license means u can keep 4 walleye with only one being over 24.8"
A days limit is also the possession limit. So 1 days catch is the most fish you can have in your possession at any time.
thats good to know thanks guys
